hadiths[127]{hadithnumber,text}:
3649,"ham se Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik zamana aayega ke ahale-Islaam ki jamatein jihad karengii to unse puchha jaeyga ke kya tumharey sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka koi sahabi bhi hai? wo kahengey ke haan hain. tab unki fateh hogi. phir aik aisa zamana aayega ke musalmanon ki jamatein jihad karengii aur us mauqe par ye puchha jaeyga ke yahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi ki sohbat uthaney waley (taaba'ii) bhi maujood hain? jawab hoga ke yahan hain aur unke zariey fateh ki dua mangi jaeygi, iske baad aik zamana aisa aayega ke musalmanon ki jamatein jihad karengii aur us waqt sawal uthega ke kya yahan koi buzurg aisey hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ke shagirdon mein se kisi buzurg ki sohbat mein rahe hon? jawab hoga ke yahan hain, to unke zariey fateh ki dua mangi jaeygi phir unki fateh hogi."
3650,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ka sabse behtreen zamana mera zamana hai, phir un logon ka jo is zamane ke baad aaeingey. phir un logon ka jo us zamane ke baad aaeingey. Imran (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke mujhey yad nahi hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne door ke baad 2 zamanon ka zikr kya ya teen kaa. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey baad aik aisi qaum paida hogi jo baghair kahey gawahi dene ke liye taiyaar ho jaya karegi aur unmein khayanat aur chori itni aam ho jaeygi ke un par kisi qism ka bharosa baqi nahi rahega aur nazrein maanengey lekin unhein pura nahi karengey (haraam maal khaa-khaa kar) un par mutaapaa aam ho jaeyga"
3651,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke behtreen zamana mera hai. phir un logon ka jo is zamane ke baad aaeingey phir un logon ka jo uske baad aaeingey. uske baad aik aisi qaum paida hogi ke gawahi deney se pahley qism unki zaban par aa jaya karegi aur qism khaney se pahley gawahi unki zaban par aa jaya karegii. Ibrahim ne bayan kya ke jab ham chhotey they, to gawahi aur ahad (ke alfaz zaban par laaney) ki wjah se hamarey badey buzurg ham ko maara kartey they."
3652,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (unke walid ( Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se aik paalaan 13 dirham mein khareedaa . phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Bara (apne betey ( se kaho ke wo mere ghar ye paalaan utha kar pahuncha dein. is par Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ye us waqt tak nahi ho sakta jab tak aap wo waqia bayan na karein ke aap aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Makka se hijrat karne ke liye) kis tarah nikley they halanke mushrekeen aap donon ko talash bhi kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha ke Makka se nikalney ke baad ham raat bhar chaltey rahe aur din mein bhi safar jari rakha. lekin jab do-pahar ho gaee to maine charon taraf nazar daudaaii ke kahin koi saaya nazar aa jaey aur ham usmein kuchh aaraam kar sakein. aakhir aik chattaan dikhai di aur maine uske paas pahunch kar dekha ke saaya hai. phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik farsh wahan bichhaa diya aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! aap ab aaraam farmaaein. chunanche aap let gaey. phir main charon taraf dekhta hua nikla ke kahin log hamari talash mein na aaey hun. phir mujh ko bakriyon ka aik charwaha dikhai diya jo apni bakriyan haanktaa hua usi chattaan ki taraf aa raha tha. wo bhi hamari tarah saaye ki talash mein tha. maine badh kar us se puchha ke ladkey tum kis ke ghulam ho. us ne Quraish ke aik shakhs ka naam liya to maine usey pehchan liya. phir maine us se puchha : kya tumhari bakriyon mein doodh hai. usne kaha ji haan. maine kaha : kya tum doodh doh saktey ho? usne kaha ke haan. chunanche maine us se kaha aur us ne apne rewad ki aik bakri baandh di. phir mere kehney par us ne uske than ke ghubaar ko jhaadaa. ab maine kaha ke apna hath bhi jhaad ley. us ne yun apna aik hath doosrey par maara aur mere liye thoda sa doodh dohaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik bartan maine pahley hi se sath ley liya tha aur uske munh ko kapdey se band kar diya tha (us mein thanda pani tha) phir maine doodh par wo pani (thandaa karne ke liye) daala itna ke wo nichey tak thanda ho gaya to usey aap ki khidmat mein lekar hazir hua. aap bhi bedaar ho chukey they. maine arz kya : doodh pi lijiye. aap ne itna piyaa ke mujhey khushi hasil ho gaee, phir maine arz kya ke ab kooch ka waqt ho gaya hai ya Rasulullah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya haan theek hai, chalo. chunanche ham aagey badhey aur Makka waley hamari talash mein they lekin Suraqa bin Malik bin Jaasham ke siwa ham ko kisi ne nahi paya, wo apne ghodey par Sawar tha, maine usey dekhtey hi kaha ke ya Rasulullah! hamara peechhaa karne wala dushman hamarey qareeb aa pahuncha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : fikr na karo. Allah Taala hamarey sath hai."
3653,"jab ham ghaare-Saur mein chhipey they, to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke agar mushrekeen ke kisi aadmi ne apne qadmon par nazar dali to wo zaroor ham ko dekh lega . is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Abu-Bakar ! un 2 ka koi kya bigaad sakta hai jinke sath tesraa Allah Taala hai.''"
3654,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya aur farmaya ke Allah Taala ne apne aik bandey ko duniya mein aur jo kuchh Allah ke paas aakhirat mein hai un donon mein se kisi aik ka ikhtiyar diya to us bandey ne wo ikhtiyar kar liya jo Allah ke paas tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) roney lagey. abu-Saeed kehtey hain ke ham ko unke roney par hairat hui ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to kisi bandey ke mutaalliq khabar de rahe hain jisey ikhtiyar diya gaya tha, lekin baat ye thi ke khud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi wo bandey they jinhein ikhtiyar diya gaya tha aur (haqeeqat mein) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ham mein sabse zyada jaanney waley they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik martaba farmaya ke apni sohbat aur maal ke zariey mujh par Abu-Bakar ka sabse zyada ehsan hai aur agar main apne rab ke siwa kisi ko jaani dost bana sakta to Abu-Bakar ko banaataa. lekin Islam ka bhai-chara aur Islam ki mohabbat unse kafi hai. dekho masjid ki taraf tamam darwazey (jo sahaba ke gharon ki taraf khultey they) sab band kar diye jaaein. sirf Abu-Bakar ka darwaza rehney do."
3655,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane hi mein jab hamein sahaba ke darmyan intikhab ke liye kaha jata to sab mein afzal aur behtar ham Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko qarar detey, phir umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko phir Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko ."
3656,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar main apni ummat ke kisi fard ko apna jaani dost bana sakta to Abu-Bakar ko banata lekin wo mere deeni bhai aur mere sathi hain.''
3657,"ham se mu'allaa-bin-Asad aur Musa ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Wuhaib ne bayan kya, unse Ayub ne ( yahi riwayat (ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar main kisi ko jaani dost bana sakta to Abu-Bakar ko banata . lekin Islam ka bhai chaara kya kam hai. ham se Quteba ne bayan kya, unse abdul-wahaab ne aur unse Ayub ne aisi hi hadis bayan ki."
3658,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke agar is ummat mein kisi ko main apna jaani dost bana sakta to Abu-Bakar ko banata .) wahi ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ye farmatey they ke daadaa, bap ki tarah hai (yani jab maiyat ka bap zinda na ho to bap ka hissa dada ki taraf lot jaeyga yani bap ki jagah dada waaris hoga ( ."
3659,aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke phir aanaa. usne kaha : agar main aaoon aur aapko na paon to? maano wo wafat ki taraf ishara kar rahi thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mujhey na pa sako to Abu-Bakar ke paas chali aana .
3660,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt dekha hai jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Islam laney walon mein sirf) panch ghulaam, 2 aurton aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur koi na tha."
3661,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apne kapdey ka kinara pakdey huey, ghutna zahir kiye huey aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye haalat dekh kar farmaya ke malum hota hai tumharey dost kisi se lad kar aaey hain. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne hazir ho kar salam kya aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere aur umr bin-Khattab ke darmyan kuchh takraar ho gaee thi aur is silsiley mein, maine jaldi mein unko sakht lafz keh diye lekin baad mein mujhey sakht nadaamat hui to maine unse maafi chaahii, ab wo mujhey maaf karne ke liye taiyaar nahi hain. isi liye mein aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Abu-Bakar ! tumhen Allah maaf kare. teen martaba aap ne ye jumla irshad farmaya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi nadaamat hui aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar pahunchey aur puchha kya Abu-Bakar ghar par maujood hain? malum hua ke nahi to aap bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap ne salam kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak ghusse se badal gaya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) dar gaey aur ghutnon ke bal baith kar arz karne lagey, ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism zyadti meri hi taraf se thi. 2 martaba ye jumla kaha, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ne mujhey tumhari taraf Nabi bana kar bheja tha aur tum logon ne mujh se kaha tha ke tum jhoot boltey ho lekin Abu-Bakar ne kaha tha ke aap sachey hain aur apni jaan w maal ke zariey unhon-ne meri madad ki thi to kya tum log mere dost ko sataanaa chhodtey ho ya nahi ? aap ne 2 baar yahi farmaya : aap ke ye farmaney ke baad phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko kisi ne nahi sataayaa."
3662,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein jange-zaatus-salaasil ke liye bheja ( Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur maine puchha ke sabse zyada mohabbat aapko kis se hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aaisha se maine poochha, aur mardon mein ? farmaya ke uske bap se. maine poochha, uske ba'd? farmaya ke umr bin-Khattab se. is tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kai aadmiyon ke naam liye."
3663,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik charwaha apni bakriyan charaa raha tha ke bhediyaa aa gaya aur rewad se aik bakri utha kar ley janey laga. charwaahey ne us se bakri chhudaanii chahi to bhediyaa bol padaa. darindon waley din mein uski rakhwaalii karne wala kon hoga jis din mere siwa aur koi charwaha na hoga. isi tarah aik shakhs bail ko is par Sawar ho kar liye ja raha tha, bail uski taraf mutwajjeh ho kar kehney laga ke meri paidaaish uske liye nahi hui hai. main to kheti baadii ke kaamon ke liye paida kya gaya hun. wo shakhs bol padaa. sub'haan-Allaah! (jaanwar aur insanon ki tarah baatein karey) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main in waaqiaat par eman laataa hun aur Abu-Bakar aur umr bin-Khattab bhii."
3664,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main so raha tha ke khuwab mein maine apne aapko aik kuwein par dekha jis par dol tha. Allah Taala ne jitna chaha maine us dol se pani kheenchaa , phir usey ibne-abi qahaafa ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ley liya aur unhon-ne aik ya 2 dol kheenchey , unke kheenchney mein kuchh kamzori si malum hui Allah unki us kamzori ko maaf farmaai . phir us dol ne aik bahut badey dol ki sura ikhtiyar kar li aur usey umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne hath mein ley liya. maine aisa taaqatwar pahlwaan aadmi nahi dekha jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki tarah dol kheench sakta. unhon-ne itna pani nikala ke logon ne apne oonton ko hauz se sairaab kar liya."
3665,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs apna kapda ( paa-jaama ya tehband wghaira) takabbur aur ghurur ki wjah se zameen par ghaseet'taa chaley to Allah Taala qiyamat ke din uski taraf nazare-rahmat se dekhega bhi nahi, is par Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke mere kapdey ka aik hissey latak jaya karta hai. albatta agar main poori tarah khayal rakhoon to wo nahi latak sakega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aap to aisa takabbur ke khayal se nahi kartey (is liye aap us hukm mein dakhil nahi hain) Moosaa ne kaha ke maine Salim se poochha, kya Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us hadis mein ye farmaya tha ke jo apni izaar ko ghaseet'tey huey chaley, to unhon-ne kaha ke maine to unse yahi suna ke jo koi apna kapda latkaaey."
3666,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne Allah ke rastey mein kisi cheez ka aik joda kharch kya ( maslan 2 rupye , 2 kapdey , 2 ghodey Allah Taala ke rastey mein diye ( to usey jannat ke darwazon se bulaya jaeyga ke aey Allah ke bandey ! idhar aa , ye darwaza behtar hai to jo shakhs namazi hoga usey Namaz ke darwazey se bulaya jaeyga, jo shakhs Mujahid hoga usey jihad ke darwazey se bulaya jaeyga, jo shakhs sadqa dene walon mein se hoga usey sadqe ke darwaze se bulaya jaeyga aur jo shakhs roze-daar hoga usey siyaam aur Rayyaan (sairaabii) ke darwazey se bulaya jaeyga Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya jis shakhs ko un tamam hi darwazon se bulaya jaeyga phir to usey kisi qism ka khof baqi nahi rahega aur puchha kya koi shakhs aisa bhi hoga jisey un tamam darwazon se bulaya jaeyga ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan aur mujhey ummeed hai ke tum bhi unhein mein se hogey aey abu-Bakar!."
3667,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jab wafat hui to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) us waqt maqam Sunh mein they. Ismail ne kaha yani awaalii ke aik gaaun mein. aap ki khabar sun kar umr (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar ye kehney lagey ke Allah ki qism Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat nahi hui. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they Allah ki qism us waqt mere dil mein yahi khayal aata tha aur main kehta tha ke Allah aapko zaroor is bimari se achchha karke uthaaeyga aur aap un logon ke hath aur paon kaat dengey (jo aap ki maut ki baatein kartey hain) itney mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) tashrif ley aaey aur andar ja kar aap ki laash Mubarak ke uper se kapda uthaya aur bosa diya aur kaha : mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hon. aap zindagi mein bhi pakeeza they aur wafat ke baad bhi aur us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, Allah Taala aap par 2 martaba maut hargiz taarii nahi karega . iske baad aap bahar aaey aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kehney lagey, aey qism khaney waale! zara thahar jaa. phir jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu shuru ki to umr (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh baith gaey."
3668,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahley Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki. phir farmaya : logo ! dekho agar koi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko poojtaa tha (yani ye samajhta tha ke wo aadmi nahi hain, wo kabhi nahi marengey) to usey malum hona chahiye ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho chuki hai aur jo shakhs Allah ki puja karta tha to Allah hamesha zinda hai usey maut kabhi nahi aaeygi. (phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sura Zumar ki ye aayat padhii)  إنك ميت وإنهم ميتون‏ ''aey paighambar! to bhi marney wala hai aur wo bhi marengey.'' aur Allah Taala ne farmaayaa وما محمد إلا رسول قد خلت من قبله الرسل أفإن مات أو قتل انقلبتم على أعقابكم ومن ينقلب على عقبيه فلن يضر الله شيئا وسيجزي الله الشاكرين'' Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf aik rasool hain. us se pahley bhi bahut se rasool guzar chukey hain. to kya agar wo wafat pa jayen ya unhein Shahid kar diya jaey to tum Islam se phir jaogey aur jo shakhs apni eidiyon ke bal phir jaey to wo Allah ko koi nuqsan nahi pahuncha sakega aur Allah an-qareeb shukr-guzar bandon ko badla dene wala hai.'' raawii ne bayan kya ke ye sun kar log phoot-phoot kar roney lagey. rawi ne bayan kya ke Ansar Saqeefa-banii-Saaida mein Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jama ho gaey aur kehney lagey ke aik ameer ham mein se hoga aur aik ameer tum (muhaajireen) mein se hoga (donon mil kar hukumat karengey) phir abu-Bakar, umr bin-Khattab aur abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah (Raziallahu anhu) unki majlis mein pahunchey . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu karni chahi lekin Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse khamosh rehney ke liye kaha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke Allah ki qism maine aisa sirf is wjah se kya tha ke maine pahley hi se aik taqreer taiyaar kar li thi jo mujhey bahut pasand aai thi phir bhi mujhey dar tha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki baraabrii us se bhi nahi ho sakegi. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne intihai balaaghat ke sath baat shuru ki. unhon-ne apni taqreer mein farmaya ke ham (Quraish) Ameer hain aur tum (jama'at ansaar) Wazeer ho. is par Hubaab-bin-Munzir (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke nahi Allah ki qism ham aisa nahi honey dengey, aik ameer ham mein se hoga aur aik ameer tum mein se hoga. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke nahi ham Ameer hain tum Wazeer ho (wjah ye hai ke) Quraish ke log sarey Arab mein sharif khandan shumaar kiye jatey hain aur unka mulk (yani Makka) Arab ke beech mein hai to ab tum ko ikhtiyar hai ya to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki bait kar lo ya abu-Ubaida-bin-Jarraah ki. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : nahi ham aap ki hi bait karengey. aap hamarey sardaar hain, ham mein sabse behtar hain aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nazdeek aap ham sabse zyada mahboob hain. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unka hath pakad liya aur unke hath par bait kar li phir sab logon ne bait ki. itney mein kisi ki awaz aai ke Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ko tum logon ne mar dala. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unhein Allah ne mar dala."
3669,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazar (wafaat se pahley) uthi aur aap ne farmaya : aey Allah ! mujhey rafeeq aalaa main ( dakhil kar) aap ne ye jumla teen martaba farmaya aur rawi ne poori hadis bayan ki. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) donon hi ke Khutbon se nafa pahuncha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko dhamkaayaa kyonke unmein kuchh munaafeqeen bhi they, isliye Allah Taala ne is tarah (ghalat afwahen phailaaney se) unko baaz rakha."
3670,aur baad mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo haq aur hidayat ki baat thi wo logon ko samjha di aur unko batla diya jo un par lazim tha (yani Islam par qaaim rehna (aur wo ye aayat tilawat kartey huey bahar aaey وما محمد إلا رسول قد خلت من قبله الرسل''Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik rasool hain aur unse pahley bhi rasool guzar chukey hain ( الشاكرين‏ ( tak.
3671,"maine apne walid ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad sabse afzal sahabi kon hain? unhon-ne batlaya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) maine puchha phir kon hain? unhon-ne batlaya , iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) hain. mujhey iska andesha hua ke ab ( phir maine puchha ke iske baad ? ( keh dengey ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) isliye maine khud kaha, iske baad aap hain? ye sun kar wo boley ke main to sirf aam musalmanon ki jamat ka aik shakhs hun."
3672,"aik safar mein ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chaley jab ham maqam beda ya maqam zaatul-Jaish par pahunchey to mera aik haar toot kar gir gaya, isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski talash ke liye wahan thahar gaey aur sahaba bhi aap ke sath thahrey lekin na us jagah pani tha aur na unke paas pani tha. log Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aa kar kehney lagey ke aap dekhtey nahi, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kya kya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko yahin rok liya hai. itney sahaba aap ke sath hain. na to yahan pani hai aur na log apne sath (pani) liye huey hain. iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) andar aaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt apna sar Mubarak meri raan par rakhey huey so rahe they. wo kehney lagey, tumhari wjah se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aur sab logon ko rukna padaa. ab na yahan kahin pani hai aur na logon ke paas pani hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh par ghussa kya aur jo kuchh Allah ko manzoor tha unhon-ne kaha aur apne hath se meri kokh mein kachokey lagaaney lagey. mein zaroor tadap uthtii magar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak meri raan par tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) soey rahe. jab subah hui to pani nahi tha aur usi mauqe par Allah Taala ne tayammum ka hukm nazil farmaya aur sab ne tayammum kya. is par Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aey aale-abu-Bakar ! ye tumhari koi pehli barkat nahi hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir ham ne jab us oont ko uthaya jis par main sawar thi to haar usi ke nichey hamein mila."
3673,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere ashaab ko bura bhala mat kaho. agar koi shakhs Uhud pahaad ke barabar bhi sona (Allah ki raah mein) kharch kar daley to unke aik mudd ghalla ke barabar bhi nahi ho sakta aur na unke aadhey mudd ke baraabar.'' Shoba ke sath us hadis ko Jareer, Abdullah-bin daawood, abu-Muawia aur muhaazir ne bhi Aamash se riwayat kya hai."
3674,"unhon-ne aik din apne ghar mein wuzu kya aur us irade se nikley ke aaj din bhar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sath na chhodunga. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir wo masjide-Nabawi mein hazir huey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke mutaalliq puchha to wahan maujood logon ne bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to tashrif ley ja chukey hain aur aap us taraf tashrif le gaey hain. chunanche main aap ke mutaalliq poochhta hua aap ke peechhey peechhey nikla aur aakhir maine dekha ke aap ( Quba ke qareeb ( Biiare-Arees (ek baagh jismein kuwan tha) mein dakhil ho rahe hain, main darwazey par baith gaya aur uska darwaza khajoor ki shakhon se bana hua tha. jab aap qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) kar chukey aur aap ne wuzu bhi kar liya to main aap ke paas gaya. maine dekha ke aap Biiare-Arees (is baagh ke kuwein) ki mundeer par baithey huey hain, apni pindliyaan aap ne khol rakhi hain aur kuwein mein paon latkaey huey hain. maine aapko salam kya aur phir wapas aa kar baagh ke darwazey par baith gaya. maine sochaa ke aaj Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka darbaan rahoonga. phir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur darwaza kholnaa chaha to maine puchha ke kon sahib hain? unhon-ne kaha ke Abu-Bakar ! maine kaha thodi der thahar jaaiye. phir main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke Abu-Bakar darwazey par maujood hain aur andar aaney ki ijazat aap se chahtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur jannat ki bashaarat bhii. mein darwaze par aaya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se maine kaha ke andar tashrif ley jaaiye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aapko jannat ki bashaarat di hai. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) andar dakhil huey aur usi kuwein ki mundeer par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dahini taraf baith gaey aur apne donon paon kuwein mein latkaa liye. jis tarah Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne latkaey huey they aur apni pindliyon ko bhi khol liya tha. phir main wapas aa kar apni jagah par baith gaya. mein aatey waqt apne bhai ko wuzu karta hua chhod aaya tha. wo mere sath aaney waley they. maine apne dil mein kaha, kash! Allah Taala falan ko khabar de deta. unki murad apne bhai se thi aur unhein yahan pahuncha deta. itney mein kisi sahib ne darwaza par dastak di maine puchha kon sahib hain? kaha ke umr bin-Khattaab. maine kaha ke thodi der ke liye thahar jaaiye, chunanche main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur salam ke baad arz kya ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) darwazey par khadey hain andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur jannat ki bashaarat bhi pahuncha do. main wapas aaya aur kaha ke andar tashrif ley jaaiye aur aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jannat ki bashaarat di hai. wo bhi dakhil huey aur aap ke sath usi mundeer par baain taraf baith gaey aur apne paon kuwein mein latkaa liye. mein phir darwazey par aa kar baith gaya aur sochta raha ke agar Allah Taala falan (unke bhaaii) ke sath khair chaahega to usey yahan pahuncha dega, itney mein aik aur sahib aaey aur darwazey par dastak di, maine puchha kon sahib hain? boley ke Usmaan-bin-Affaan, maine kaha thodi der ke liye ruk jaaiye, mein aap ke paas aaya aur maine aapko unki itlaa di. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur aik museebat par jo unhein pahuncheygii jannat ki bashaarat pahuncha do. main darwazey par aaya aur maine unse kaha ke andar tashrif ley jaaiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aapko jannat ki bashaarat di hai, aik museebat par jo aapko pahunchegii. wo jab dakhil huey to dekha chabootre par jagah nahi hai is liye wo dusri taraf Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney baith gaey. Sharik ne bayan kya ke Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne kaha maine us se unki qabron ki taaweel li hai (ke isi tarah banengii)."
3675,"jab Nabi Karim (sl), abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar Uhud pahaad par chadhey to Uhud kanp uthaa, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Uhud! qarar pakad ke tujh par aik nabii, aik siddeeq aur 2 Shahid hain.''"
3676,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aik kuwein par) khuwab mein) khada us se pani kheench raha tha ke mere paas Abu-Bakar aur umr bhi pahunch gaey. phir Abu-Bakar ne dol ley liya aur aik ya 2 dol kheenchey, unke kheenchney mein kamzori thi aur Allah Taala unki maghfirat karega. phir Abu-Bakar ke hath se dol umr ne ley liya aur unke hath mein pahunchtey hi wo aik bahut badey dol ki shakl mein ho gaya. maine koi himmat wala aur bahaadur insan nahi dekha jo itni Husain tadbeer aur mazbut quwwat ke sath kaam karne ka aadi ho, chunanche unhon-ne itna pani kheenchaa ke logon ne oonton ke pani pilaaney ki jaghein bhar liin, Wahab ne bayan kya ke) العطن ( oonton ke baithney ki jagah ko kehtey hain, Arab log boltey hain, oont sairaab huey ke) wahin ( baith gaey."
3677,"main un logon ke sath khada tha jo umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye duaein kar rahe they, us waqt unka janaaza charpai par rakha hua tha, itney mein aik sahib ne mere peechhey se aa kar mere shaanon par apni kohniyaan rakh diin aur) umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko mukhaatab karke ( kehney lagey Allah aap par raham kare. mujhey to yahi ummeed thi ke Allah Taala aapko aap ke donon sathiyon ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath ( dafn ( karaaeyga, mein aksar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko yun farmatey suna karta tha ke ''main aur Abu-Bakar aur umr they'', ''maine aur Abu-Bakar aur umr ne ye kaam kya'', ''main aur Abu-Bakar aur umr gaey'' isliye mujhey yahi ummeed thi ke Allah Taala aapko un hi donon buzurgon ke sath rakhega . maine jo mud kar dekha to wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they."
3678,"maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se mushrekeene-Makka ki sabse badi zaalimaana harkat ke barey mein puchha jo unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ki thi to unhon-ne batlaya ke maine dekha ke Aqba bin abi mueet Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya. aap us waqt Namaz padh rahe they, us bad-bakht ne apni chadar aap ki gardan Mubarak mein daal kar khinchi jis se aap ka gala badi sakhti ke sath phans gaya. itney mein Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur us bad-bakht ko dafa' kya aur kaha kya tum aik aisey shakhs ko qatl karna chahtey ho jo ye kehta hai ke mera parwardigar Allah Taala hai aur wo tumharey paas apne parwardigar ki taraf se khuli hui daleelein bhi lekar aaya hai."
3679,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main ( khuwab mein) jannat mein dakhil hua to wahan maine abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Rameesaa ko dekha aur maine qadmon ki awaz suni to maine puchha ye kon sahib hain? bataya gaya ke ye Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) hain aur maine aik mahal dekha uske samney aik aurat thi, maine puchha ye kis ka mahal hai? to bataya ke ye umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka hai. mere dil mein aaya ke andar dakhil ho kar usey dekhoon, lekin mujhey umr ki ghairat yad aai (aur isliye andar dakhil nahi hua). is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne rotey huey kaha mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hun, ya Rasulullah! kya main aap par ghairat karunga."
3680,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main soyaa hua tha ke maine khuwab mein jannat dekhi . maine dekha ke aik aurat aik mahal ke kinarey wuzu kar rahi hai. maine puchha ye mahal kis ka hai? to farishton ne jawab diya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) kaa. phir mujhey unki ghairat w hamiiyat yad aai aur main wahin se lot aaya. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ro diye aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya main aap par bhi ghairat karoonga?
3681,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine khuwab mein doodh piyaa, itna ke main doodh ki sairaabii dekhney laga jo mere naakhun ya nakhunon par bah rahi hai, phir maine piyala umr ko de diya. sahaba ne puchha : ya Rasulullah! is khuwab ki tabeer kya hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iski tabeer ilm hai."
3682,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine khuwab mein dekha ke main aik kuwein se aik achchha bada dol kheench raha hun, jis par '' lakdi ka charkh '' laga hua hai, phir Abu-Bakar aaey aur unhon-ne bhi aik ya 2 dol kheenchey magar kamzori ke sath aur Allah unki maghfirat kare. phir umr aaey aur unke hath mein wo dol aik bahut badey dol ki sura ikhtiyar kar gaya. maine un jaisa mazbut aur baa-azmat shakhs nahi dekha jo itni mazbootii ke sath kaam kar sakta ho. unhon-ne itna kheenchaa ke log sairaab ho gaey aur apne oonton ko pilaa kar unke thikaanon par ley gaey. ibne- Juber ne kaha ke) abqarii (ka mana umda aur) zaraabee (aur ( abqarii ( sardaar ko bhi kehtey hain ( hadis main ( abqarii ( se yahi murad hai) Yahya bin Ziyad Faree ne kaha, ( zaraabee ( un bichhonon ko kehtey hain jinke haashiye baareek , phailey huey bahut kasarat se hotey hain."
3683,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se andar aaney ki ijazat chahi . us waqt aap ke paas Quraish ki chand auratein ( ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se) baithi baatein kar rahi thin aur aap ki awaz par apni awaz unchi kartey huey aap se naan w nafqa mein zyadti ka mutalba kar rahi thin. joon hi umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ijazat chahi to wo tamam khadi ho kar pardey ke peechhey jaldi se bhag khadi huin. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat di aur wo dakhil huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa rahe they. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hamesha khush rakhey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey un aurton par hansi aa rahi hai jo abhi mere paas baithi hui thin, lekin tumhari awaz suntey hi sab pardey ke peechhey bhag gain . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! darnaa to unhein aap se chahiye tha. phir unhon-ne (aurton se) kaha aey apni jaanon ki dushmanon! tum mujh se to dartii ho aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi darteen, aurton ne kaha ke haan, aap theek kehtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke muqaabley mein aap kahin zyada sakht hain. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey ibne- khitaab! us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, agar shaitan tumhen kisi rastey par chalta dekhta hai to usey chhod kar wo kisi doosrey rastey par chal padta hai."
3684,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke Islam laney ke baad phir hamein hamesha izzat hasil rahi.
3685,"jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko (shahaadat ke baad) unki charpai par rakha gaya to tamam logon ne laash Mubarak ko gher liya aur unke liye ( Allah se) dua aur maghfirat talab karne lagey, laash abhi uthai nahi gaee thi, mein bhi wahin maujood tha. usi haalat mein achcha aik sahib ne mera shana pakad liya, maine dekha to wo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) they, phir unhon-ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye dua'ae-rahmat ki aur (unki laash ko mukhaatab karke) kaha : aap ne apne baad kisi bhi shakhs ko nahi chhoda ke jisey dekh kar mujhey ye tamanna hoti ke iske amal jaisa amal kartey huey main Allah se ja miloon aur Allah ki qasam! mujhey to (pahley se) yaqin tha ke Allah Taala aapko aap ke donon sathiyon ke sath hi rakhega. mera ye yaqin is wjah se tha ke maine aksar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban Mubarak se ye alfaz suney they ke ''main, Abu-Bakar aur umr gaey. main, Abu-Bakar aur umr dakhil huey. main, Abu-Bakar aur umr bahar aaey.''"
3686,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Uhud pahaad par chadhey to aap ke sath abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, pahaad larazney laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne paon se usey maara aur farmaya ''Uhud ! thehra reh ke tujh par aik nabii, aik siddeeq aur 2 Shahid hi to hain.''"
3687,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se apne walid umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke kuchh halaat poochhey, jo maine unhein bata diye to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad maine kisi shakhs ko Deen mein itni zyada koshish karne wala aur itna zyada data nahi dekha aur ye khubiyan umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) par khatm ho gaiin."
3688,"aik sahib (zul-khuwesra ya abu-Moosa) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se qiyamat ke barey mein puchha ke qiyamat Kab qaaim hogii? is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne qiyamat ke liye taiyaarii kya ki hai? unhon-ne arz kya kuchh bhi nahi, siwa iske ke main Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tumhara hashr bhi unhiin ke sath hoga jin se tumhen mohabbat hai.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke hamein kabhi itni khushi kisi baat se bhi nahi hui jitni aap ki ye hadis sun kar hui ke ''tumhaaraa hashr unhiin ke sath hoga jin se tumhen mohabbat hai.'' Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mohabbat rakhta hun aur unse apni us mohabbat ki wjah se ummeed rakhta hun ke mera hashr unhiin ke sath hoga, agarche mein un jaisey amal na kar saka."
3689,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum se pehli ummaton mein muhaddas hua kartey they, aur agar meri ummat mein koi aisa shakhs hai to wo umr hain. Zakariiyaa-bin-Zaayda ne apni riwayat mein Sad se ye badhaya hai ke unse abu-Salma ne bayan kya aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum se pahley Bani-Israeel ki ummaton mein kuchh log aisey hua kartey they ke Nabi nahi hotey they aur uske bawajud Farishtey unse kalam kya kartey they aur agar meri ummat mein koi aisa shakhs ho sakta hai to wo umr hain. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne padha (من نبي wla محدث)."
3690,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik charwaha apni bakriyan charaa raha tha ke aik bhediye ne uski aik bakri pakad li. charwaahey ne uska peechhaa kya aur bakri ko us se chhudaa liya. phir bhediyaa uski taraf mutwajjeh ho kar bola : darindon ke din uski hifazat karne wala kon hoga? jab mere siwa uska koi charwaha na hoga. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) is par bol uthey : sub'haan-Allaah! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main is waqia par eman laya aur Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhii. halanke wahan Abu-Bakar w umr (Raziallahu anhu) maujood nahi they.
3691,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine khuwab mein dekha ke kuchh log mere samney pesh kiye gaey jo qamees pahney huey they unmein se kuchh ki qamees sirf seeney tak thi aur kuchh ki us se bhi chhoti aur mere samney umr pesh kiye gaey to wo itni badi qamees pahney huey they ke chaltey huey ghisat'tii thi. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap ne iski tabeer kya li ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Deen murad hai.
3692,"jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi kar diye gaey to aap ne badi be chainii ka izhar kya. us mauqe par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se tasalli ke taur par kaha ke aey ameerul-momineen ! aap is darja ghabraa kyon rahe hain. aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein rahe aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ka pura haq ada kya aur phir jab aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se juda huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aap se khush aur razi they, iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat uthai aur unki sohbat ka bhi aap ne pura haq ada kya aur jab juda huey to wo bhi aap se razi aur khush they. aakhir mein musalmanon ki sohbat aapko hasil rahi. unki sohbat ka bhi aap ne pura haq ada kya aur agar aap unse juda huey to ismein koi shuba nahi ke unhein bhi aap apne se khush aur razi hi chhodengey. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Ibne-Abbas ! tum ne jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat ka aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raza w khushi ka zikr kya hai to yaqinan ye sirf Allah Taala ka aik Fazal aur ehsan hai jo usney mujh par kya hai. isi tarah jo tum ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat aur unki khushi ka zikr kya hai to ye bhi Allah Taala ka mujh par Fazal w ehsan tha. lekin jo ghabraahat aur pareshani mujh par tum taarii dekh rahe ho wo tumhari wjah se aur tumharey sathiyon ki fikr ki wjah se hai. aur Allah ki qism ! agar mere paas zameen bhar sona hota to Allah Taala ke azab ka saamnaa karne se pahley uska fidya de kar us se nijat ki koshish karta. Hammad-bin-Zaid ne bayan kya, unse Ayub ne bayan kya, unse ibne-abi-Mulaika ne aur unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke main umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. phir aakhir tak yahi hadis bayan ki."
3693,"main Madina ke aik baagh (Beeare-Raees) main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath tha ke aik sahib ne aa kar darwaza khulwaya , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unke liye darwaza khol do aur unhein jannat ki bashaarat suna do, maine darwaza khola to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they. maine unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farmaney ke mutabiq jannat ki khushkhabri sunai to unhon-ne is par Allah ki hamd ki, phir aik aur sahib aaey aur darwaza khulwaya . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par bhi yahi farmaya ke darwaza unke liye khol do aur unhein jannat ki bashaarat suna do, maine darwaza khola to umr (Raziallahu anhu) they, unhein bhi jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad ki itlaa sunai to unhon-ne bhi Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan ki. phir aik teesrey aur sahib ne darwaza khulwaayaa. unke liye bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke darwaza khol do aur unhein jannat ki bashaarat suna do un mushkilon aur aazmaaishon ke baad jin se unhein ( duniya mein) waasta padega . wo Usman (Raziallahu anhu) they. jab maine unko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke irshad ki itlaa di to unhon-ne Allah ki hamd w sana ke baad farmaya ke Allah Taala hi madad karne wala hai."
3694,ham aik martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. aap us waqt umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ka hath apne hath mein liye huey they.
3695,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik baagh (Beeare-Raees) ke andar tashrif le gaey aur mujh se farmaya ke main darwaza par pahra deta rahoon. phir aik sahib aaey aur ijazat chahi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein ijazat de do aur jannat ki khushkhabri bhi suna do, wo Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) they. phir doosrey aik aur sahib aaey aur ijazat chahi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein bhi ijazat de do aur jannat ki khushkhabri suna do, wo umr (Raziallahu anhu) they. phir teesrey aik aur sahib aaey aur ijazat chaahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der ke liye khamosh ho gaey phir farmaya ke unhein bhi ijazat de do aur (duniyaa mein) aik aazmaish se guzarney ke baad jannat ki bashaarat bhi suna do, wo Usman ghanii (Raziallahu anhu) they. Hammaad-bin-Salma ne bayan kya, ham se Aasim ahwaal aur Ali-bin-Hakam ne bayan kya, unhon-ne abu-Usman se suna aur wo abu-Musa se isi tarah bayan kartey they, lekin Aasim ne apni is riwayat mein ye zyada kya hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt aik aisi jagah baithey huey they jiske andar pani tha aur aap apne donon ghutney ya aik ghutna kholey huey they lekin jab Usman (Raziallahu anhu) dakhil huey to aap ne apne ghutney ko chipa liya."
3696,"tum Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se unke bhai Waleed ke muqaddime mein (jisey Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Kufa ka governer banaya tha) kyon guftgu nahi kartey, log us se bahut naraz hain. chunanche main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya, aur jab wo Namaz ke liye bahar tashrif laey to maine arz kya ke mujhey aap se aik zarurat hai aur wo hai aap ke sath aik khair-khaahii! is par Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : bhaley aadmi tum se (main Allah ki panah chahta hun) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : main samajhta hun ke Mamar ne yun riwayat kya, main tujh se Allah ki panah chahta hun. main wapas un donon ke paas gaya, itney mein Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaasid mujh ko bulaney ke liye aaya. main jab uske sath Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to unhon-ne malum farmaya ke tumhari khair-khahi kya thi? maine arz kya : Allah Sub'haanahu w taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath bheja aur un par kitab nazil ki aap bhi un logon mein shamil they jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki dawat ko qabool kya tha. aap ne 2 hijratein kin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat uthai aur aap ke tareeqey aur sunnat ko dekha, lekin baat ye hai ke log Waleed ki bahut shikaayatein kar rahe hain. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par puchha : tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh suna hai? maine arz kya ke nahi. lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadison aik kunwari ladki tak ko uske tamam pardon ke bawajud jab pahunch chuki hain to mujhey kyon na malum hotiin. is par Usman ne farmaya : ammaa ba'd; beshak Allah Taala ne Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haq ke sath bheja aur main Allah aur uske rasool ki dawat ko qabool karne walon mein bhi tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis dawat ko lekar bhejey gaey they main is par poorey taur se eman laya aur jaisa ke tum ne kaha 2 hijratein bhi kin. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein bhi raha hun aur aap se bait bhi ki hai. to Allah ki qism maine kabhi aap ke hukm se sartaabii nahi ki. aur na aap ke sath kabhi koi dhokaa kya, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne aapko wafat di. iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi mera yahi mamla raha aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath bhi yahi mamla raha to kya jabke mujhey unka jaa-nashiin bana diya gaya hai to mujhey wo huquq hasil nahi hongey jo unhein they? maine arz kya ke kyon nahi, aap ne farmaya ke phir un baton ke liye kya jawaz reh jata hai jo tum logon ki taraf se mujhey pahunchti rehti hain lekin tum ne jo Waleed ke halaat ka zikr kya hai, inshaAllah ham uski saza jo waajibii hai usko dengey. phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya aur unse farmaya ke Waleed ko had lagaaein. chunanche unhon-ne Waleed ko assii kode had ke lagaey."
3697,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Uhud pahaad par chadhey aur aap ke sath Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, to pahaad kaanpney laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ''Uhud thahar jaa.'' mera khayal hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey apne paon se maara bhi tha ke tujh par aik nabii, aik siddeeq aur 2 Shahid hi to hain."
3698,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein ham Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke barabar kisi ko nahi qarar detey they. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko phir Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba par ham koi bahas nahi kartey they aur kisi ko aik doosrey par fazeelat nahi detey they. is hadis ko Abdullaah-bin-Saaleh ne bhi Abdul-Azeez se riwayat kya hai.
3699,"Misr walon mein se aik naam naa-maaloom aadmi aaya aur Haj Baitullah kya, phir kuchh logon ko baithey huey dekha to usne puchha ke ye kon log hain? kisi ne kaha ke ye qureshi hain. us ne puchha ke unmein buzurg kon sahib hain? logon ne bataya ke ye Abdullah-bin-Umar hain. us ne poochha. aey ibne-Umar ! main aap se aik baat poochhna chahta hun. ummeed hai ke aap mujhey bataaengey. kya aapko malum hai ke Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Uhud ki ladai se raahe-faraar ikhtiyar ki thi? ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke haan, aisa hua tha. phir unhon-ne poochha. kya aapko malum hai ke wo badr ki ladai mein Sharik nahi huey they? jawab diya ke haan aisa hua tha. us ne puchha kya aapko malum hai ke wo (baite-rizwan mein bhi Sharik nahi they. jawab diya ke haan ye bhi sahi hai. ye sun kar uski zaban se nikla Allahu-akbar to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke qareeb aa jao, ab main tumhen in waaqiaat ki tafseel samjhaaunga. Uhud ki ladai se faraar ke mutaalliq main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala ne unhein maaf kar diya hai. badr ki ladai mein Sharik na honey ki wjah ye hai ke unke nikah main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sahibzadi thin aur us waqt wo bimar thin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke tumhen (mareeza ke paas thaharney ka ( itna hi ajr w sawab milega jitna us shakhs ko jo badr ki ladai mein Sharik hoga aur usi ke mutabiq maale-ghanimat se hissey bhi milega aur (baite-rizwan mein Sharik na honey ki wjah ye hai ke us mauqe par wadi Makka mein koi bhi shakhs (musalmanon mein se) Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se zyada izzat wala aur baa-asar hota to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usi ko unki jagah wahan bhejtey, yahi wjah hui thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ( Quraish se baatein karne ke liye) Makka bhej diya tha aur jab (baite-rizwan ho rahi thi to Usman (Raziallahu anhu) Makka ja chukey they, us mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne daahiney hath ko utha kar farmaya tha ke ye Usman ka hath hai aur phir usey apne doosrey hath par hath rakh kar farmaya tha ke ye bait Usman ki taraf se hai. iske baad ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne sawal karne waley shakhs se farmaya ke jaa, in baton ko hamesha yad rakhna. ham se Musaddad ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Saeed ne, unse Qatada ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Uhud pahaad par chadhey aur aap ke sath abu-Bakar, umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, to pahaad kaanpney laga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ahad thahar ja mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey apne paon se maara bhi tha ke tujh par aik nabii, aik siddeeq aur 2 Shahid hi to hain."
3700,"maine umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakhmi honey se chand din pahley Madina mein dekha ke wo Huzefa bin Yamaan aur Usman bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khadey they aur unse ye farma rahe they ke (Iraaq ki araazii ke liye, jiska intizam khilafat ki taraf se unke sipurd kya gaya tha) tum logon ne kya kya hai? kya tum logon ko ye andesha to nahi hai ke tum ne zameen ka itna tax laga diya hai jiski gunjaaish na ho. un logon ne jawab diya ke ham ne un par khiraaj (Tax) ka itna hi baar daala hai jisey ada karne ki zameen mein taqat hai, usmein koi zyadti nahi ki gaee hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke dekho phir samajh lo ke tum ne aisi jama to nahi lagai hai jo zameen ki taqat se bahar ho. rawi ne bayan kya ke un donon ne kaha ke aisa nahi honey paaeyga, iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke agar Allah Taala ne mujhey zinda rakha to main Iraq ki bewa aurton ke liye itna kar doonga ke phir mere baad kisi ki mohtaaj nahi rahengii. rawi Amr-bin-Memoon ne bayan kya ke abhi is guftgu par chotha din hi aaya tha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) zakhmi kar diye gaey. Amr-bin-Memoon ne bayan kya ke jis subah ko aap zakhmi kiye gaey, main (fajr ki Namaz ke intizar mein) saf ke andar khada tha aur mere aur unke darmyan Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur koi nahi tha umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki aadat thi ke jab saf se guzartey to farmatey jatey ke safain seedhi kar lo aur jab dekhtey ke safon mein koi kharabi nahi reh gayi hai tab aagey (musalley par) badhtey aur takbeer kehtey. aap (fajr ki Namaz ki) pehli rakaat mein aam taur se sura Yusuf ya sura Nahal ya itni hi lambi koi sura padhtey, yahan tak ke log jama ho jatey. us din bhii aap ne takbeer hi kahi thi ke maine suna, aap farma rahe hain ke mujhey qatl kar diya ya kuttey ne kaat liya. Abu-Lu-Lu ne aapko zakhmi kar diya tha. iske baad wo bad-bakht apna 2 dhaarii khanjar liye daudney laga aur daain aur baain jidhar bhi phirtaa to logon ko zakhmi karta jata. is tarah us ne 13 aadmiyon ko zakhmi kar diya jin mein saat (7) hazraat ne shahadat paaii. musalmanon mein se aik sahib ( Hittan naam ke) ne ye soorate-haal dekhi to unhon-ne is par apni chadar daal di. Mina us bad-bakht ko jab yaqin ho gaya ke ab pakad liya jaeyga to usne khud apna bhi gala kaat liya, phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ka hath pakad kar unhein aagey badha diya (Amr-bin-Memoon ne bayan kya ke) jo log umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb they unhon-ne bhi wo soorate-haal dekhi jo main dekh raha tha lekin jo log masjid ke kinarey par they (peechhey ki safon mein) to unhein kuchh malum nahi ho sakaa, albatta chunkey umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki qirat (namaz mein) unhon-ne nahi suni to Subhan-Allah ! sub'haan-Allaah! kehtey rahe. aakhir Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne logon ko bahut halki Namaz padhai. phir jab log Namaz se paltey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ibne-Abbaas! dekho mujhey kis ne zakhmi kya hai? Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne thodi der ghoom phir kar dekha aur aa kar farmaya ke Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghulam (Abu-Lu-Lu) ne aapko zakhmi kya hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum farmaya, wahi jo kaareegar hai? jawab diya ke ji haan, is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya Allah usey barbad karey maine to usey achi baat kahi thi (jiska us ne ye badla diyaa) Allah Taala ka shukr hai ke usne meri maut kisi aisey shakhs ke hathon nahi muqaddar ki jo Islam ka muddaii ho. tum aur tumharey walid (Abbaas (rz)) iske bahut hi khaahishmand they ke ajamii ghulam Madina mein zyada se zyada laey jaaein. yun bhi unke paas ghulam bahut they, is par Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, agar aap farmaein to ham bhi kar guzriin. maqsad ye tha ke agar aap chaahein to ham (Madina mein muqeem ajamii ghulaamon ko) qatl kar daalein. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ye intihai ghalat fikr hai, khususan jabke tumhari zaban mein wo guftgu kartey hain, tumharey qible ki taraf rukh karke Namaz ada kartey hain aur tumhari tarah Haj kartey hain. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko unke ghar utha kar laya gaya aur ham aap ke saath-saath aaey. aisa malum hota tha jaisey logon par kabhi us se pahley itni badi museebat aai hi nahi thi, kuchh to ye kehtey they ke kuchh nahi hoga. ( achchhey ho jaeinge (aur kuchh kehtey they ke aap ki zindagi khatre mein hai. iske baad khajoor ka pani laya gaya. usey aap ne piyaa to wo aap ke pet se bahar nikal aaya. phir doodh laya gaya usey bhi joon hi aap ne piyaa zakhm ke rastey wo bhi bahar nikal aaya. ab logon ko yaqin ho gaya ke aap ki shahadat yaqeeni hai. phir ham andar aagey aur log aap ki tareef bayan karne lagey, itney mein aik naujawaan andar aaya aur kehney laga aey ameerul-momineen ! aapko khushkhabri ho Allah Taala ki taraf se aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat uthaaii. shuruaat mein Islam laney ka sharf hasil kya jo aapko malum hai. phir aap khaleefa banaey gaey aur aap ne poorey insaf se hukumat ki, phir shahadat paaii. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya main to is par bhi khush tha ke in baton ki wjah se barabar par mera mamla khatm ho jata, na sawab hota aur na azaab. jab wo naujawaan janey laga to uska tehband ( izaar ( latak raha tha, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya us ladkey ko mere paas wapas bula lao (jab wo aaey to (aap ne farmaya : mere bhatijey ! ye apna kapda uper uthaey rakho ke is se tumhara kapda bhi zyada dinon chalega aur tumharey rab se taqwa ka bhi baais hai. Mina aey Abdullah-bin-Umar ! dekho mujh par kitna qarz hai? jab logon ne aap par qarz ka shumaar kya to taqriban chhiyaasii ( 86 ( hazaar nikla . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par farmaya ke agar ye qarz aale-Umar ke maal se ada ho sakey to unhi ke maal se usko ada karna warna phir banii-adii-bin-Ka'b se kahnaa, agar unke maal ke baad bhi adaaeygi na ho sakey to Quraish se kahnaa, unke siwa kisi se imdaad na talab karna aur meri taraf se is qarz ko ada kar dena. achchha ab Ummul-Momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan jao aur unse arz karo ke umr ne aap ki khidmat mein salam arz kya hai. ameerul-momineen (mere naam ke saath) na kahnaa, kyonke ab main musalmanon ka ameer nahi raha hun, to unse arz karna ke Umar-bin-Khattab ne aap se apne donon sathiyon ke sath dafn honey ki ijazat chahi hai. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar) salam kya aur ijazat lekar andar dakhil huey. dekha ke aap baithi ro rahi hain. phir kaha ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aapko salam kaha hai aur apne donon sathiyon ke sath dafn honey ki ijazat chahi hai, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine is jagah ko apne liye muntakhab kar rakha tha lekin aaj main unhein apne par tarjeeh doongii, phir jab ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) wapas aaey to logon ne bataya ke Abdullah aagey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke mujhey uthaao. aik sahib ne sahara de kar aapko uthaayaa. aap ne malum kya kya khabar laaey? kaha ke jo aap ki tamanna thi aey ameerul-momineen! umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya al-hamdulillah. us se aham cheez ab mere liye koi nahi reh gaee thi. lekin jab meri wafat ho chukey aur mujhey utha kar) dafn ke liye) ley chalo to phir mera salam unse kehna aur arz karna ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap se ijazat chahi hai. agar wo mere liye ijazat de dein tab to wahan dafn karna aur agar ijazat na dein to musalmanon ke qabristaan mein dafn karna. iske baad Ummul-Momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) aaiin. unke sath kuchh dusri khawaateen bhi thin, jab ham ne unhein dekha to ham uth gaey. aap umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb aaein aur wahan thodi der tak aansu bahaatii rahen. phir jab mardon ne andar aaney ki ijazat chahi to wo makan ke androonii hisse mein chali gain aur ham ne unke roney ki awaz suni phir logon ne arz kya ameerul-momineen ! khilafat ke liye koi wasiiyat kar dijiye , farmaya ke khilafat ka main un hazraat se zyada aur kisi ko mustahiq nahi paata ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni wafat tak jin se razi aur khush they phir aap ne Ali, Usmaan, Zubair, Tal'ha, Sad aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ka naam liya aur ye bhi farmaya ke Abdullah-bin-Umar ko bhi sirf mashware ki had tak Sharik rakhna lekin khilafat se unhein koi sarokaar nahi rahega. jaisey aap ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taskeen ke liye ye farmaya ho. phir agar khilafat Sad ko mil jaey to wo iske ahal hain aur agar wo na ho sakein to jo shakhs bhi khaleefa ho wo apne zamaanae-khilaafat mein unka ta'awun hasil karta rahe. Mina kyonke maine unko (koofa ki governary se) naa-ahlii ya kisi khayanat ki wjah se nahi hataya hai, aur umr ne farmaya : main apne baad hone-waale khaleefa ko muhajireen awwaleen ke barey mein wasiiyat karta hun ke wo unke huquq pahchaaney aur unke ehtiraam ko malhooz rakhey aur main apne baad hone-waale khaleefa ko wasiiyat karta hun ke wo Ansar ke sath behtar mamla karey jo daarul-Hijrat aur daarul-eimaan (Madina Munawra ( main ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tashrif aawrii se pahley se) muqeem hain. (khaleefa ko chahiye (ke wo unke nekon ko nawaazey aur unke buron ko maaf kar diya karey aur main hone-waale khaleefa ko wasiiyat karta hun ke shehri aabadi ke sath bhi achchha mamla rakhey ke ye log Islam ki madad, maal jama karne ka zariia' aur (Islam ke) dushmanon ke liye aik museebat hain aur ye ke unse wahi wsool kya jaey jo unke paas faazil ho aur unki khushi se liya jaey aur main hone-waale khaleefa ko badviyon ke sath bhi achchha mamla karne ki wasiiyat karta hun ke wo asl Arab hain aur Islam ki jad hain aur ye ke unse unka bachaa-khuchaa maal wsool kya jaey aur unhiin ke mohtajon mein taqseem kar diya jaey aur main hone-waale khaleefa ko Allah aur uske rasool ke ahad ki nigahdaasht ki (jo Islami hukumat ke tehet ghair muslimon se kya hai) wasiiyat karta hun ke unse kiye gaey ahad ko pura kya jaey, unki hifazat ke liye jang ki jaey aur unki haisiyat se zyada un par bojh na daala jaaey. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ho gaee to ham wahan se unko lekar ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (ke hujre ki taraf aaey. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne salam kya aur arz kya ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne ijazat chahi hai. Ummul-Momenin ne kaha unhein yahin dafn kya jaey. chunanche wo wahin dafn huey, phir jab log dafn se farigh ho chukey to wo jamat (jinke naam umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne wafat se pahley bataaey they) jama hui Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne kaha : tumhen apna mamla apne hi mein se teen aadmiyon ke sipurd kar dena chahiye is par Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine apna mamla Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sipurd kya. Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main apna mamla Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke sipurd karta hun aur Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine apna mamla Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ke sipurd kya. iske baad Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Usman aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko mukhaatab karke ( kaha ke aap donon hazraat mein se jo bhi khilafat se apni Bara't (bezaarii) zahir karey ham usi ko khilafat dengey aur Allah uska nigraan w nigahbaan hoga aur Islam ke huquq ki zimme-dari is par lazim hogi. har shakhs ko ghaur karna chahiye ke uske khayal mein kon afzal hai. is par ye donon hazraat khamosh ho gaey to Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya aap hazraat is intikhab ki zimme-dari mujh par daltey hain, Allah ki qism ke main aap hazraat mein se usi ko muntakhab karunga jo sab mein afzal hoga. un donon hazraat ne kaha ke ji haan, phir aap ne un donon mein se aik ka hath pakda aur farmaya ke aap ki qaraabat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hai aur shuruaat mein Islam laney ka sharf bhii. jaisa ke aapko khud hi malum hai, to Allah aap ka nigraan hai ke agar main aapko khaleefa bana dun to kya aap adl w insaf se kaam lengey aur agar Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaleefa bana dun to kya aap unke ehkaam sunengey aur unki itaat karengey? iske baad doosrey sahib ko tanhai mein le gaey aur unse bhi yahi kaha aur jab unse wada ley liya to farmaya : aey Usmaan! apna hath badhaaiye. chunanche unhon-ne unse bait ki aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi unse bait ki, phir ahale-Madeena aaey aur sab ne bait ki."
3701,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par bayan farmaya ke kal main aik aisey shakhs ko Islami jhanda doonga jiske hath par Allah Taala fateh inayat farmaeyga, rawi ne bayan kya ke raat ko log ye sochtey rahe ke dekhiye jhanda kisey milta hai, jab subah hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sab hazraat (jo sarkarda they) hazir huey, sab ko ummeed thi ke jhanda unhein hi milega, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, Ali-bin abi-Talib kahan hain? logon ne bataya ke unki aankhon mein dard hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir unke yahan kisi ko bhej kar bulwa lo, jab wo aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki aankh mein apna thook daala aur unke liye dua farmai, us se unhein aisi shifa hasil hui jaisey koi marz pahley tha hi nahi, chunanche aap ne jhanda unhiin ko inayat farmaya, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main unse itna ladunga ke wo hamarey jaisey ho jayen (yani musalman bin jaaein) aap ne farmaya : abhi yun hi chaltey raho, jab unke maidan mein utro to pahley unhein Islam ki dawat do aur unhein bataao ke Allah ke un par kya huquq wajib hain, Allah ki qism agar tumharey zariey Allah Taala aik shakhs ko bhi hidayat dedey to wo tumharey liye surkh oonton (ki daulat ( se behtar hai."
3702,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aankh dukhney ki wajah se nahi aa sakey they, phir unhon-ne sochaa main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang mein Sharik na ho sakun ! chunanche ghar se nikley aur aap ke lashkar se ja miley, jab us raat ki Sham aai jiski subah ko Allah Taala ne fateh inayat farmai thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kal main aik aisey shakhs ko jhanda doonga ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya ke kal) aik aisa shakhs jhandey ko lega jisse Allah aur uske rasool ko mohabbat hai ya aap ne ye farmaya ke jo Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hai aur Allah Taala uske hath par fateh inayat farmaeyga, ittifaq se Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aa gaey, halanke unke aaney ki hamein ummeed nahi thi logon ne bataya ke ye hain Ali (Raziallahu anhu) . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jhanda unhein de diya, aur Allah Taala ne unke hath par khaibar ko fateh kara diya."
3703,"ye falan shakhs iska ishara ameere-Madeena (Marwaan-bin-Hakam) ki taraf tha, member par khadey hokar Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bura-bhala kehta hai, abu-Hazim ne bayan kya ke Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha kya kehta hai? us ne bataya ke unhein ''abu-Turaab'' kehta hai. is par Sehal hansney lagey aur farmaya ke Allah ki qasam! ye naam to unka Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rakha tha aur khud Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko us naam se zyada apne liye aur koi naam pasand nahi tha. ye sun kar maine is hadis ke jaanney ke liye Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) se khahish zahir ki aur arz kya : aey abu-Abbaas ! ye waqia kis tarah se hai? unhon-ne bayan kya ke aik martaba Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaey aur phir bahar aa kar masjid mein let rahe, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se) malum farmaya, tumharey chacha ke betey kahan hain? unhon-ne bataya ke masjid mein hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid mein tashrif laaey, dekha to unki chadar peeth se nichey gir gaee hai aur unki kamar par achi tarah se khaak lag chuki hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mitti unki kamar se saaf farmaney lagey aur boley, utho aey abu-Turaab utho ! ( 2 martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ( ."
3704,"aik shakhs Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein aaya aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq poochha, ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki khoobiyon ka zikr kya, phir kaha ke shayad ye baatein tumhen buri lagi hongii, usne kaha ji haan. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Allah teri naak khaak aalooda karey phir us ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq poochha, unhon-ne unki bhi khoobiyon ka zikr kiye aur kaha ke Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka gharaana Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khandan ka bahut hi zyada umda gharaana hai, phir kaha shayad ye baatein bhi tumhen buri lagi hongii, usne kaha ke ji haan, Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) boley Allah teri naak khaak aalooda karey, jaa, aur mera jo bigaadnaa chahey bigaad lenaa, kuchh kami na karna."
3705,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se) chakkii peesney ki takleef ki shikayat ki, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey to Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aap ke paas aaiin lekin aap maujood nahi they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se unki mulaqat hui to unse iske barey mein unhon-ne baat ki jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke aaney ki itlaa di, is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud hamarey ghar tashrif laaey, us waqt ham apne bistaron par let chukey they, maine chaha ke khada ho jaun lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yun hi letey raho, iske baad aap ham donon ke darmyan baith gaey aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qadmon ki thandak apne seeney mein mehsus ki. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum logon ne mujh se jo talab kya hai kya main tumhen us se achi baat na bataaoon, jab tum soney ke liye bistar par leto to chauntis martaba Allaahu-akbar, tentis martaba Subhan-Allah aur tentis martaba alhamdulillah padh liya karo, ye amal tumharey liye kisi khaadim se behtar hai."
3706,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke kya tum is par khush nahi ho ke tum mere liye aisey ho jaisey Musa (Alaihissalam) ke liye Harun (Alaihissalam) they.
3707,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Iraq walon se kaha ke jis tarah tum pahley faisla kya kartey they ab bhi kya karo kyonke main ikhtilaf ko bura janta hun. us waqt tak ke sab log jama ho jayen ya main bhi apne sathiyon (abu-Bakar w umr (rz)) ki tarah duniya se chala jaun, Ibne-Sirin (Rahmatullahi-alaih) kaha kartey they ke aam log (rawaafiz) jo Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat (sheikhain ki mukhalifat mein) bayan kartey hain wo hargiz jhooti hain."
3708,"log kehtey hain ke Abu-Hurera bahut hadisein bayan karta hai, halanke pet bharney ke baad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath har waqt rehta tha, main khameerii roti na khata aur na umda libaas pehnta tha (yani mera waqt ilm ke siwa kisi dusri cheez ke hasil karne mein na jaataa) aur na meri khidmat ke liye koi falan ya fulaanii thi balke main bhook ki shiddat ki wjah se apne pet se patthar baandh liya karta. kuchh waqt mein kisi ko koi aayat isliye padh kar iska matlab poochhta tha ke wo apne ghar ley ja kar mujhey khana khilaa de, halanke mujhey is aayat ka matlab malum hota tha, miskinon ke sath sabse behtar sulook karne waley Jafar bin-abii-Taalib (Raziallahu anhu) they, hamein apne ghar ley jatey aur jo kuchh bhi ghar mein maujood hota wo ham ko khilaatey. kabhi-kabhi to aisa hota ke sirf shehad ya ghi ki kupii hi nikal kar latey aur usey ham phaad kar usmein jo kuchh hota usey hi chaat letey."
3709,jab Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sahibzadey ko salam kartey to yun kaha kartey السلام عليك ya ابن ذي الجناحينaey 2 paron waley buzurg ke sahibzadey tum par salam ho. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha hadis mein jo ( جناحين‏) ka lafz hai us se murad 2 goshey ( koney ( hain.
3710,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) qahat ke zamaney mein Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ko aagey badha kar barish ki dua karatey aur kehtey ke aey Allah pahley ham apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se barish ki dua karatey they, to hamein sairaabii ata karta tha aur ab ham apne Nabi ke chacha ke zariey barish ki dua kartey hain. isliye hamein sairaabii ata farmaa. rawi ne bayan kya ke iske baad khub barish hui."
3711,"Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan apna aadmi bhej kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se milney wali meeraas ka mutalba kya jo Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Fai ki sura mein di thi. yani aap ka mutalba Madina ki us jaaidaad ke barey mein tha jiski aamadni se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khair ke kaamon mein kharch kartey they, aur isi tarah fidak ki jaaidaad aur khaibar ke khums ka bhi mutalba kya."
3712,"hamari meeraas nahi hoti. ham ( anbiya ( jo kuchh chhod jatey hain wo sadqa hota hai aur ye ke aale-Muhammad ke kharchey usi maal mein se poorey kiye jayen magar unhein ye haq nahi hoga ke khaney ke ilawa aur kuchh tasarruf karein aur mein, Allah ki qism ! aap ke sadqey mein jo aap ke zamaney mein hua kartey they unmein koi radd w badal nahi karunga balke wahi nizaam jari rakhoonga jaisey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaaim farmaya tha. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey aur kehney lagey : aey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ham aap ki fazeelat w martabe ka iqrar kartey hain. iske baad unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se apni qaraabat ka aur apne haq ka zikr kya, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki qaraabat walon se sulook karna mujh ko apni qaraabat walon ke sath sulook karne se zyada pasand hai."
3713,unhon-ne kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khayal aapke ahale-bait mein rakho.
3714,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Fatima mere jism ka tukda hai, isliye jisne usey nahaq naraz kya, usne mujhey naraz kya."
3715,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko apne us marz ke mauqe par bulaya jis mein aap ki wafat hui, phir aahista se koi baat kahi to wo roney lagiin, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulaya aur aahista se koi baat kahi to wo hansney lagiin, Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir maine unse iske mutaalliq poochha."
3716,"to unhon-ne bataya ke pahley mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aahista se ye farmaya tha ke wo apni usi bimari mein wafat pa jaaeinge, main is par roney lagi phir mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aahista se farmaya ke aap ke ahale-bait mein sabse pahley mein aap se ja miloongii, is par main hansi thi."
3717,"jis saal nakseer phootney ki bimari phoot padi thi us saal Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ko itni sakht nakseer phootii ke aap Haj ke liye bhi na ja sakey, aur) zindagi se maayoos ho kar) wasiiyat bhi kar di, phir unki khidmat mein Quraish ke aik sahib gaey aur kaha ke aap kisi ko apna khaleefa bana dein. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum farmaya : kya ye sabki khahish hai, unhon-ne kaha ji haan. aap ne puchha ke kisey banaaun? is par wo khamosh ho gaey. iske baad aik doosrey sahib gaey. mera khayal hai ke wo Haris they, unhon-ne bhi yahi kaha ke aap kisi ko khaleefa bana dein, aap ne unse bhi puchha kya ye sab ki khahish hai? unhon-ne kaha : ji haan, aap ne puchha : logon ki raey kis ke liye hai? is par wo bhi khamosh ho gaey, to aap ne khud farmaya : ghaaliban Zuber ki taraf logon ka rujhaan hai? unhon-ne kaha ji haan, phir aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai mere ilm ke mutabiq bhi wahi unmein sabse behtar hain aur bila shubah wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nazron mein bhi unmein sabse zyada mahboob they."
3718,"main Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein maujood tha ke itney mein aik sahib aaey aur kaha ke kisi ko aap apna khaleefa bana dijiye, aap ne malum farmaya kya iski khahish ki ja rahi hai? unhon-ne bataya ke ji haan, Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf logon ka rujhaan hai, aap ne is par farmaya theek hai, tum ko bhi malum hai ke wo tum mein behtar hain, aap ne teen martaba ye baat dohraaii."
3719,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya har Nabi ke hawaarii hotey hain aur mere hawaarii Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) hain.
3720,"jange-Ehzaab ke mauqe par mujhey aur Umar-bin abi Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ko aurton mein chhod diya gaya tha (kyonke ye donon hazraat bachchey they) maine achcha dekha ke Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) (aap ke walid ( apne ghodey par Sawar bani Qureza ( yahudiyon ke aik qabila ki) taraf aa ja rahe hain. 2 ya 3 martaba aisa hua, phir jab main wahan se wapas aaya to maine arz kya, abba jaan ! maine aapko kai martaba aatey-jaatey dekha. unhon-ne kaha : betey! kya waqei tum ne bhi dekha hai? maine arz kya : ji haan, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke kon hai jo banu-Quraiza ki taraf ja kar unki (naql w harkat ke mutaalliq) itlaa mere paas la sakey. is par main wahan gaya aur jab main (khabar lekar) wapas aaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (khushi ke maarey) apne waalidain ka aik sath zikr karke farmaya ke ''mere maan-baap tum par fidaa hon.''"
3721,jange-Yarmook ke mauqe par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ne Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha aap hamla kyon nahi kartey taake ham bhi aap ke sath hamla karein. chunanche unhon-ne un ( roomiyon ( par hamla kya. is mauqe par unhon-ne (Roomiyon ne) aap ke 2 badey zakhm kandhey par lagaey. darmyan mein wo zakhm tha jo badr ke mauqe par aapko laga tha. Urwa ne kaha ke (ye zakhm itney gahrey they ke achchhey ho janey ke baad) mein bachpan mein un zakhmon ke andar apni ungliyan daal kar khelaa karta tha.
3722,kuchh un jangon mein jin main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud Sharik huey they (Uhud ki jang mein) aap ke sath Talha aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur koi baqi nahi raha tha.
3723,kuchh un jangon mein jin main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud Sharik huey they (Uhud ki jang mein) aap ke sath Talha aur Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur koi baqi nahi raha thaa.
3724,maine Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka wo hath dekha hai jis se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) jange-Uhud mein) hifazat ki thi wo bilkul bekaar ho chuka tha.
3725,jange-Uhud ke mauqe par mere liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne waalidain ko aik sath jama karke yun farmaya ke mere maan-baap tum par fidaa hon.
3726,mujhey khub yad hai. maine aik zamaney mein musalmanon ka teesra hissey apne aapko dekha. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha Islam ke teesrey hissey se ye murad hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sirf teen musalman they jin mein tesraa musalman main tha.
3727,"jis din mein Islam laayaa, isi din doosrey (sab se pahley Islam mein dakhil hone-waale hazraat sahaba ( bhi Islam mein dakhil huey hain aur main saat (7) din tak usi taur par raha ke main Islam ka teesra fard tha. ibne-abii-Zaayda ke sath us hadis ko abu-Usama ne bhi riwayat kya."
3728,"Arab mein sabse pahley Allah ke rastey mein, maine teer andazi ki thi (ibtidaae-Islaam mein) ham Nabi Karim (sl), ke sath is tarah jangon mein shirkat kartey they ke hamarey paas darakht ke patton ke siwa khaney ke liye kuchh bhi na hota tha, us se hamein oont aur bakriyon ki tarah ijaabat hoti thi. yani mili hui nahi hoti thi. lekin ab banii-Asad ka ye haal hai ke Islami ehkaam par amal mein mere andar aib nikaaltey hain (agar ( aisa ho to main bilkul mahroom aur be-naseeb hi raha aur mere sab kaam barbad ho gaey. hua ye tha ke bani Asad ne umr (Raziallahu anhu) se Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki chughlii khaaii thi. ye kaha tha ke wo achi tarah Namaz bhi nahi padhtey."
3729,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne abu-Jahal ki ladki ko (jo musalman thiin) paighaame-nikaah diya, uski itlaa jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko hui to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaiin aur arz kya ke aap ki qaum ka khayal hai ke aapko apni betiyon ki khaatir (jab unhein koi takleef de) kisi par ghussa nahi aataa. ab dekhiye ye Ali abu-Jahal ki beti se nikah karna chahtey hain, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko khitab farmaya : maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khutba padhtey suna. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ammaa ba'd! maine abul-Aas-bin Rabe se (Zainab (Raziallahu anhu) ki, aap ki sabse badi saahibzaadii) shadi karaai to unhon-ne jo baat bhi kahi usmein wo sachey utrey aur bila shubah Fatima bhi mere ( jism ka ( aik tukda hai aur mujhey ye pasand nahi ke koi bhi usey takleef de. Allah ki qism ! Rasulullah ki beti aur Allah Taala ke aik dushman ki beti aik shakhs ke paas jama nahi ho saktiin. chunanche Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne is shadi ka irada tark kar diya Muhammad-bin Amr-bin-halhala ne ibne-Shahab se ye izafa kya hai, unhon-ne Ali-bin Husain se aur unhon-ne Miswar (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne bani Abd-Shams ke apne aik daamaad ka zikr kya aur huqooqe-daamaadii ki adaaeygi ki tareef farmai. phir farmaya ke unhon-ne mujh se jo baat bhi kahi sachchii kahi aur jo wada bhi kya pura kar dikhaayaa."
3730,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik fauj bheji aur uska ameer Usama-bin-Zaid ko banaya. unke ameer banaey janey par kuchh logon ne aetraz kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar aaj tum iske ameer banaey janey par aetraz kar rahe ho to is se pahley iske bap ke ameer banaey janey par bhi tum ne aetraz kya tha aur Allah ki qasam! wo (Zaid (Raziallahu anhu)) amaarat ke mustahiq they aur mujhey sabse zyada azeez they. aur ye (Usaama (Raziallahu anhu)) ab unke baad mujhey sabse zyada azeez hain.
3731,"aik qiyaafa shanaas (shakl-soorat dekhka andaza lagaaney wala) mere yahan aaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt wahin tashrif rakhtey they aur Usama-bin-Zaid aur Zaid-bin-Haarisa (eik chadar mein) letey huey they. (munh aur jism ka Sara hissey qadmon ke siwa chipa hua tha) us qiyaafa shanaas ne kaha ke ye paon kuchh, kuchh se nikley huey malum hotey hain. (yani bap betey ke hain) qiyaafa shanaas ne phir bataya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske us andaza par bahut khush huey aur phir aap ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se bhi ye waqia bayan farmaayaa."
3732,"Quraish makhzoomiya aurat ke mamley ki wjah se bahut ranjeeda they. unhon-ne ye faisla aapas mein kya ke Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwaa, jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko intihai azeez hain (is aurat ki sifarish ke liye) aur kon jur'at kar sakta hai!"
3733,"maine Zohri se makhzoomiya ki hadis poochhi to wo mujh par bahut ghussa ho gaey. maine is par Sufiyan se puchha ke phir aap ne kisi aur zariey se is hadis ki riwayat nahi ki? unhon-ne bayan kya ke Ayub bin-Musa ki likhi hui aik kitab mein, maine ye hadis dekhi. wo Zohri se riwayat kartey they, wo Urwa se, wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ke bani makhzoom ki aik aurat ne chori kar li thi. Quraish ne (apni majlis mein) sochaa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein us aurat ki sifarish ke liye kon ja sakta hai? koi uski jur'at nahi kar sakaa, aakhir Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne sifarish ki to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Bani-Israeel mein ye dastoor ho gaya tha ke jab koi sharif aadmi chori karta to usey chhod detey aur agar koi kamzor aadmi chori karta to uska hath kaat'tey. agar aaj Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne chori ki hoti to main uska bhi hath kaat'taa."
3734,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik din aik sahib ko masjid mein dekha ke apna kapda aik koney mein phaila rahe they. unhon-ne kaha dekho ye kon sahib hain? kash! ! ye mere qareeb hotey. aik shakhs ne kaha aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya aap unhein nahi pahchaantey? ye Muhammad-bin Usama (Raziallahu anhu) hain. ibne-diinaar ne bayan kya ke ye suntey hi Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne apna sar jhukaa liya aur apne hathon se zameen kuredney lagey phir boley agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein dekhtey to yaqinan aap unse mohabbat farmatey.
3735,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein aur Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko pakad letey aur farmatey : aey Allah ! to inhein apna mahboob bana ke main inse mohabbat karta hun.
3736,"Hajjaj-bin aiman bin umme-aiman ko Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha (namaz mein) unhon-ne rukoo aur sajda poori tarah nahi ada kya, (aiman-ibn-umme-aiman, Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ki maa ki taraf se bhai they, aiman (Raziallahu anhu) qabila Ansar ke aik fard they) to ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke (namaz ( dobara padh lo."
3737,"wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke Hajjaj-bin aiman (masjid ke) andar aaey na unhon-ne rukoo poori tarah ada kya tha aur na sajda. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse farmaya ke Namaz dobara padh lo. phir jab wo janey lagey to unhon-ne mujh se puchha ke ye kon hain? maine arz kya Hajjaj-bin aiman ibne- umme-aiman hain. is par aap ne kaha agar unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dekhtey to bahut azeez rakhtey, phir aap ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki Usama (Raziallahu anhu) aur umme-aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ki tamam aulad se mohabbat ka zikr kya. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne bayan kya ke mujh se mere kuchh asaatza ne bayan kya aur unse Sulaiman ne ke Umme- aiman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko god liya tha."
3738,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab maujood they, to jab bhi koi shakhs koi khuwab dekhta to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usey bayan karta. mere dil mein bhi ye tamanna paida ho gaee ke main bhi koi khuwab dekhun aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan karun. mein un dinon kunwaaraa tha aur nau-umr bhi tha. main aap ke zamaney mein masjid mein soyaa karta tha to maine khuwab mein 2 farishton ko dekha ke mujhey pakad kar dozakh ki taraf ley gaey. maine dekha ke wo bal daar kuwein ki tarah pech dar pech thi. kuwein hi ki tarah iske bhi 2 kinarey they aur uske andar kuchh aisey log they jinhein main pehchanta tha. main usey dekhtey hi kehney laga dozakh se main Allah ki panah mangta hun, dozakh se main Allah ki panah mangta hun. iske baad mujh se aik doosrey Farishtey ki mulaqat hui, usne mujh se kaha ke khof na khaa, maine apna ye khuwab Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kya."
3739,Hafsa ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mera khuwab bayan kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah bahut achchha ladka hai. kash! ! raat mein wo tahajjud ki Namaz padha karta. Salim ne bayan kya ke Abdullah iske baad raat mein bahut kam soyaa kartey they.
3740,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya tha ke Abdullah nek aadmi hai.
3741,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya tha ke Abdullah nek aadmi hai.
3742,"main jab Sham (Syria) aaya to maine 2 rakaat Namaz padh kar ye dua ki ke aey Allah ! mujhey koi nek sathi ata farmaa. phir main aik qaum ke paas aaya aur unki majlis mein baith gaya, thodi hi der baad aik buzurg aaey aur mere paas baith gaey. maine puchha ye kon buzurg hain? logon ne bataya ke ye abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) hain. is par maine arz kya ke maine Allah Taala se dua ki thi ke koi nek sathi mujhey ata farma, to Allah Taala ne aapko mujhey inayat farmaya, unhon-ne malum kya, tumhara watan kahan hai? maine arz kya Kufa hai. unhon-ne kaha kya tumharey yahaan (ابن أم عبد صاحب النعلين والوساد والمطهرة) (yaanii Abdullah-bin-Masood (rz)) nahi hain? kya tumharey yahan wo nahi hain jinhein Allah Taala apne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zabani shaitan se panah de chuka hai ke wo unhein kabhi ghalat rastey par nahi ley ja sakta. ( murad Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se thi) kya tum mein wo nahi hain jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bataaey huey bahut se bhedon ke haamil hain jinhein unke siwa aur koi nahi janta. (yani Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu)) iske baad unhon-ne malum farmaya : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) aayat ( والليل إذا يغشى‏ ( ki tilawat kis tarah kartey hain? maine unhein padh kar sunai ke) والليل إذا يغشى * والنهار إذا تجلى * والذكر والأنثى‏ ( is par unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud apni zaban se mujhey bhi isi tarah yad karaya tha."
3743,"Alqama (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) mein tashrif le gaey aur masjid mein ja kar ye dua ki. aey Allah ! mujhey aik nek sathi ata farma, chunanche aapko abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat naseeb hui. abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum kya : tumhara talluq kahan se hai? arz kya ke Kufa se, is par unhon-ne kaha : kya tumharey yahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke raaz daar nahi hain ke un raazon ko unke siwa aur koi nahi janta ? (unki murad abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) se thi) unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya ji haan maujood hain, phir unhon-ne kaha kya tum mein wo shakhs nahi hain jinhein Allah Taala ne apne Nabi ki zabani shaitan se apni panah di thi. unki murad Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se thi. maine arz kya ke ji haan wo bhi maujood hain, iske baad unhon-ne malum kya ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) aayat ( والليل إذا يغشى * والنهار إذا تجلى‏ ) ki qirat kis tarah kartey they? maine kaha ke wo وما خلق ke baghair ( والذكر والأنثى‏ ( padha kartey they. is par unhon-ne kaha ye Sham (Syria) waley hamesha us koshish mein rahe ke us aayat ki tilawat ko jis tarah maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha us se mujhey hata dein."
3744,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har ummat mein ameen hotey hain aur is ummat ke ameen abu-Ubaida bin-Jarraah hain.
3745,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ahal Najran se farmaya ke main tumharey yahan aik ameen ko bhejoonga jo sahii maanon mein ameen hoga. ye sun kar tamam sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ko shauq hua lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Ubaida (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhejaa.
3746,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif farma they aur Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke pahlu mein they, aap kabhi logon ki taraf mutwajjeh hotey aur phir Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf aur farmatey : mera ye betaa sardaar hai aur ummeed hai ke Allah Taala iske zariey musalmanon ki 2 jamaton mein suleh karaaeyga."
3747,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein aur Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko pakad kar ye dua kartey they ( اللهم إني أحبهما فأحبهما ( ''aey Allah ! mujhey unse mohabbat hai to bhi unse mohabbat rakh. '' ( أو كما قال‏ (
3748,jab Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ka sar Ubaidullaah-bin-Ziyaad ke paas laya gaya aur aik tasht mein rakh diya gaya to wo bad-bakht is par lakdi se maarney laga aur aap ke husno-khoobsoortii ke barey mein bhi kuchh kaha (ke maine us se zyada khoobsurat chehra nahi dekhaa) is par Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Husain (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sabse zyada mushabeh (similar) they. unhon-ne (وسمة‏ (ka khizaab istemal kar rakha tha.
3749,Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) aap ke kaandhey Mubarak par they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye farma rahe they ''aey Allah ! mujhey is se mohabbat hai to bhi us se mohabbat rakh. ''
3750,"aap Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko uthaey huey hain aur farma rahe hain : mere bap un par fidaa hon, ye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushabeh (similar) hain, Ali se nahi aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) muskuraa rahe they."
3751,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki khushnoodii ( ko aap ke ahale-bait ke sath (muhabbat w khidmat ke zariie') talash karo.
3752,Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se zyada aur koi shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mushabeh (similar) nahi tha.
3753,"mere khayal mein ye puchha tha ke agar koi shakhs (ehraam ki haalat mein) makkhii mar de to usey kya kaffara dena padega? is par Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : Iraq ke log makkhii ke barey mein sawal kartey hain jabke yahi log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nawaasey ko qatl kar chukey hain, jinke barey mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke donon (nawaasey Hasan w Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) duniya mein mere 2 phool hain."
3754,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey sardaar hain aur hamarey sardaar ko unhon-ne aazad kya hai, unki murad Bilal habshi (Raziallahu anhu) se thi."
3755,Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : agar aap ne mujhey apne liye khareedaa hai to phir apne paas hi rakhiye aur agar Allah ke liye khareedaa hai to phir mujhey aazad kar dijiye aur Allah ke rastey mein amal karne dijiye.
3756,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne seeney se lagaya aur farmaya ''aey Allaah! isey hikmat ka ilm ata farmaa.''
3757,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi itlaa ke pahunchne se pahley Zaid, Jafar aur ibn-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat ki khabar sahaba ko suna di thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab Islami jhande ko Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) liye huey hain aur wo Shahid kar diye gaey, ab Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jhanda utha liya aur wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey, ab ibne-rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne jhanda utha liya aur wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu jari they phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aur aakhir Allah ki talwaaron mein se aik talwaar (Khaalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu)) ne jhanda utha liya aur Allah Taala ne unke hath par musalmanon ko fateh inayat farmai."
3758,"Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan Abdullah-bin-Masood ka zikr hua to unhon-ne kaha, main unse hamesha mohabbat rakhoonga kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna hai ke char ashkhaas se Quran seekho. Abdullaah-bin-Mas'ood, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shuruaat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se hi ki aur abu-Huzaifa ke Maula Saalim, Ubai-bin-Kab aur Muaz-bin-Jabal se, unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey poori tarah yad nahi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pahley Ubai-bin-Kab ka zikr kya ya Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) kaa."
3759,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zabaane-mubaarak par koi bura kalima nahi aata tha aur na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaat se ye mumkin tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke tum mein sabse zyada azeez mujhey wo shakhs hai jiske aadaat w akhlaq sabse umda hon.
3760,"aur aap ne farmaya ke Quran Majeed char aadmiyon se seekho, Abdullaah-bin-Mas'ood, abu-Huzaifa ke Maula Saalim, Ubai-bin-Kab aur Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) se."
3761,"main Sham (Syria) pahuncha to sabse pahley maine 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur ye dua ki ke aey Allaah! mujhey kisi (nek) sathi ki sohbat se Faizyaabii ki taufeeq ata farmaa. chunanche maine dekha ke aik buzurg aa rahe hain, jab wo qareeb aagey to maine sochaa ke shayad meri dua qabool ho gaee hai. unhon-ne malum farmaya : aap ka watan kahan hai? maine arz kya ke main Kufa ka rehney wala hun, is par unhon-ne farmaya : kya tumharey yahaan (صاحب النعلين والوساد والمطهرة)(Abdullaah-bin-Mas'ood (rz)) nahi hain? kya tumharey yahan wo sahabi nahi hain jinhein shaitan se (Allah ki) panah mil chuki hai. (yani Ammar bin-Yaasir (rz)) kya tumharey yahan sr-basta raazon ke jaanney waley nahi hain ke jinhein unke siwa aur koi nahi janta ( phir malum farmaya ( ibne- Umme- abd ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (rz)) aayat ( والليل‏ ( ki qirat kis tarah kartey hain? maine arz kya ke (والليل إذا يغشى * والنهار إذا تجلى * والذكر والأنثى‏ (aap ne farmaya ke mujhey bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud apni zaban Mubarak se isi tarah sikhaya tha. lekin ab Sham (Syria) waley mujhey is tarah qirat karne se hataanaa chahtey hain."
3762,"sahaba main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aadaat w akhlaq aur taur tareeq mein sabse zyada qareeb kon se sahabi they? taake ham unse seekhein, unhon-ne kaha akhlaaq, taur tareeq aur seerat w aadat mein ibne-umme-abd se zyada Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se qareeb aur kisi ko main nahi samajhtaa."
3763,"maine abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se suna : unhon-ne bayan kya ke main aur mere bhai Yaman se (Madina taiba) hazir huey aur aik zamaney tak yahan qiyam kya, ham us poorey arsa mein yahi samajhtey rahe ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke gharaaney hi ke aik fard hain, kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) aur unki walida ka ( kasrat se ( aana jana ham khud dekha kartey they."
3764,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne isha ke baad witr ki Namaz sirf aik rakaat padhi wahin Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke Maula ( Kureb ( bhi maujood they, jab wo Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to ( ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik rakaat witr ka zikr kya ( is par unhon-ne kaha : koi harj nahi hai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat uthai hai."
3765,"Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya ke ameerul-momineen Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutaalliq aap kya farmatey hain, unhon-ne witr ki Namaz sirf aik rakaat padhi hai? unhon-ne kaha ke wo khud faqeeh hain."
3766,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tum log aik khas Namaz padhtey ho, ham log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein rahe aur ham ne kabhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us waqt Namaz padhtey nahi dekha, balke aap ne to us se mana farmaya tha. Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki murad Asr ke baad 2 rakaat Namaz se thi (jisey us zamaney mein kuchh log padhtey they)."
3767,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Fatima mere jism ka aik tukda hai jisne usey naraz kya usne mujhey naraz kya.
3768,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik din farmaya ''aey Aaish ye Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) tashrif farma hain aur tumhen salam kehtey hain'' maine is par jawab diya w-alahissalaam warahmatullahi wabarkaatuh! aap wo cheez dekhtey hain jo mujh ko nazar nahi aati (aap ki murad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se thi).
3769,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mardon main to bahut se kaamil paida huey lekin aurton mein Maryam binte- Imran , firaun ki biwi aasiya ke siwa aur koi kaamil paida nahi hui, aur Aaisha ki fazeelat aurton par aisi hai jaisey sareed ki fazeelat Baqiiya tamam khaanon par hai.''"
3770,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki fazeelat baqi aurton par aisi hai jaisey sareed ki fazeelat aur tamam khaanon par.
3771,"Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) bimar padiin to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) iyaadat ke liye aaey aur arz kya : ummul-momeneen! aap to sachey janey jaanewaale ke paas ja rahi hain, yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar ke paas (aalame-barzakh mein unse mulaqat murad thi)."
3772,"jab Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Ammar aur Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko Kufa bheja tha taake logon ko apni madad ke liye taiyaar karein to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse Khattab kartey huey farmaya tha : mujhey bhi khub malum hai ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi hain is duniya mein bhi aur aakhirat mein bhi, lekin Allah Taala tumhen aazmaanaa chahta hai ke dekhey tum Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki ittaba (pairvi) kartey ho (jo bar-haq khaleefa hain) ya Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki."
3773,"(Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang mein janey ke liye) aap ne (apni bahan) Asma (Raziallahu anha) se aik haar udhaar ley liya tha, ittifaq se wo rastey mein kahin gum ho gaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey talash karne ke liye chand sahaba ko bhejaa, is doran mein Namaz ka waqt ho gaya to un hazraat ne baghair wuzu ke Namaz padh li, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap se sura haal ke mutaalliq arz kya. iske baad tayammum ki aayat nazil hui. is par Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tumhen Allah Taala jazaaye khair de, Allah ki qasam! tum par jab bhi koi marhala aaya to Allah Taala ne us se nikalney ki sabeel tumharey liye paida kar di, aur tamam musalmanon ke liye bhi usmein barkat paida farmai."
3774,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne maut ke marz mein bhi paak beeviyon ki baari ki pabandi farmatey rahe albatta ye malum farmatey rahe ke kal mujhey kis ke yahan thaharnaa hai? kyonke aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ke khaahishmand they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab mere yahan qiyam ka din aaya to aapko sukoon hua.
3775,"log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tohfey bhejney main Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ka intizar kya kartey they. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke meri saukanein sab Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gain aur unse kaha : Allah ki qism log jaan-bojh kar apne tohfey us din bhejtey hain jis din Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki baari hoti hai, ham bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki tarah apne liye fayda chahti hain, isliye tum Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaho ke aap logon ko farma dein ke main jis bhi biwi ke paas rahoon jiski bhi baari ho usi ghar mein tohfey bhej diya karo. Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne ye baat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney bayan ki, aap ne kuchh bhi jawab nahi diya. unhon-ne dobara arz kya jab bhi jawab na diya, phir teesri baar arz kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Umme-Salma ! Aaisha ke barey mein mujh ko na sataao . Allah ki qism ! tum mein se kisi biwi ke lihaf mein (jo mein odhtaa hun sotey waqt) mujh par wahi nazil nahi hoti haan ( Aaisha ka maqam ye hai) unke lihaf mein wahi nazil hoti hai."
